  • Page 238: Printer Modes (Overview)

    5.3 Printer Modes (Overview) The DocuPrint N24/N32/N40/N3225/N4025 printer has four modes of operation, each with its own set of options. • On Line Mode • Power Saver Mode • Diagnostic Mode • Menu Mode 5.3.1 On Line On Line is the printer's normal operating mode. In this mode, the printer is On Line, under the control of the System Controller, and ready to generate output.
